"However, if the bus brakes suddenly obviously the physical laws are valid.
The same as in a city bus or tram.
The safety of the hostess must be solved by the internal regulations of the carrier, "he says and also thinks that from the point of view of the law this problem is unsolved.
Jančura is ready to cancel this service
Student Agency is the only carrier that offers the hostess service.
He employs two hundred in it.
