"However, the moment I have the impression that the position of stewardess is risky, then I will suppress it.
Coffee and newspapers can meet you, passengers, upon entering.
It would even save expenses," he says.
In the interest of safety is why Asiana lacks hostesses in its vehicles, according to Alexej Litvin, who runs a small line compared to SA.
"We don't have flight attendants, we are against them from the beginning.
